{"tid":1434914,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦又有野同大家講，勇武入黎！","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:25:31.000Z","uid":127439,"like":41,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"fda8387204ce65a5643844f10f13b12f314f083d","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"無錯，係需要少少手段氹你地入黎睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日太多分化post大家可能睇到呢啲內容嘅post就覺得又係黎分化割蓆。<br />\n但我希望大家可以認真loop返呢幾日政府嘅行動黎睇呢篇文。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住! 呢場係長期戰，<br />\n係要有效地將民主戰勝歸來。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入返個正題<br />\n事源前日有朋友見到林鄭落區後，想託我喺連登同你地講少少野，我自己消化一輪後，表示認同，所以就出左呢個post，希望大家真係可以花少少時間睇下: <br />\n<br />\n//以下純粹係我個人意見。<br />\n林鄭擺明唔會再傾反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至五大訴求<br />\n大家當然可以遊行<br />\n但勇武派唔好再做任何衝擊送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無留意前日林鄭已經落區<br />\n咁代表咩呢？<br />\n即係佢自己都知民望低無可低<br />\n與其同你班人戀戰<br />\n落區反而可以令佢民意回升<br />\n點解呢？<br />\n因為五大訴求綑綁嚟講，政府一定唔會傾<br />\n咁唔傾會點？<br />\n勇武派繼續破壞<br />\n結局咪即係攬炒囉！<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">一般百姓係咪想攬炒</span><br />\n咁就一定唔會啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭落區咪擺明話你知<br />\n你一係同佢地攬炒<br />\n一係就信我呢個爛政府<br />\n我係爛嫁喇，但你未至於無法生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人已經見到破壞帶嚟既影響<br />\n咁梗係唔會想攬炒<br />\n就會寧願接受爛政府</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家可以點做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非上場</span><br />\n民間發佈會繼續有<br />\n減少政府抹黑<br />\n實實在在做D幫到大眾既野<br />\n等佢地知道政府無能<br />\n而你地係真係愛香港<br />\n因為愛香港就無理由破壞香港<br />\n<br />\n我怕既係大家以為D人覺醒<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實中間既民意仍然佔大多數</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">林鄭落區扮聽民意</span><br />\n對比<span style=\"font-size: large;\">示威者破壞</span><br />\n就會<span style=\"font-size: large;\">變相加佢分</span><br />\n到時無壓倒性贏建制<br />\n大家只會徒勞無功<br />\n兼秋後算帳</span><br />\n<br />\n我既方法未必有效<br />\n但諗諗點<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令林鄭落區呢下無得加分</span></span><br />\n從而要佢回應件事//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，朋友提大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再搞交通</span></span>，會影響到孕婦同長期病患者，只要有任何一個人因為咁出事，民意一定會逆轉。<br />\n佢仲話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家政府既玩法似足佔中</span></span>，依家去到<span style=\"color: red;\">四點鐘許sir，係咁開記者會</span>。大家一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">諗諗點解林鄭要玩落區</span></span>，你就明佢已經改變策略，你唔好理佢真聽民意定係扮，但佢肯做個姿態出嚟。<br />\n同埋CCTVB太入屋，播示威者破壞，又播林鄭落區，D港豬就會以為林鄭肯改。<br />\n<br />\n唔知道你地睇完之後點諗，可能會覺得呢個post係想分化，割席，但絕對唔係！<br />\n至少我到今時今刻都唔係，好想你地明白依家無論你地作出咩類型既衝擊，對林鄭抑或警察都起唔到任何作用，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與其推勇武同街坊出去死，比警察濫捕，和理非麻煩不如浮面啦。</span></span><br />\n我都覺得依家民間記者會係個好開始，唔好比其他人單一接收政府所有抹黑示威者既言論，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不妨再係多區擺街站播出黎宣傳。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，梁天琦致香港人既信，我相信大部分人都有睇，唔知大家點去理解，正如<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「光復香港 時代革命」都可以有好多詮譯</span></span>。我想輕輕節錄一段比大家再仔細思考一下...<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: <br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒</span>，這乃是人之常情。但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，更要始終保持理性的思考。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己</span></span>，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命與之對賭，而是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在患難中的忍耐、老練和盼望</span></span>。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求 缺一不可</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b595af983111bfb8f734a14d7f38e37b6007f076","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:04:18.000Z","msg":"agger，不過樓主小心比啲分化撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e2a1f3bf63de296a04f79183c1f8e60589add5","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"而家係連登理性分析下就比人屌分化同三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f2f02e965f32b4557aadee100fcabef244554a","tid":1434914,"uid":2419,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨 我唔撚會睇你打乜"},{"pid":"d6007cd74dd4a7ea9893ead3018bbfcf8819cdb7","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e2a1f3bf63de296a04f79183c1f8e60589add5","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"而家係連登理性分析下就比人屌分化同三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"勇武係前線時嘅決定真係唔到我地插嘴<br />\n但希望係休息嘅時候可以跳返出框框<br />\n環觀返個狀況再做部處同決定要點樣繼續有效抗爭"},{"pid":"cb5c842881a8494e4196b903b4c3cafcdf210b57","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6007cd74dd4a7ea9893ead3018bbfcf8819cdb7","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e2a1f3bf63de296a04f79183c1f8e60589add5","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"而家係連登理性分析下就比人屌分化同三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"勇武係前線時嘅決定真係唔到我地插嘴<br />\n但希望係休息嘅時候可以跳返出框框<br />\n環觀返個狀況再做部處同決定要點樣繼續有效抗爭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"啱呀，但係而家叫人唔好衝機場都會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f5f41585bc8f6045ff0537013b683fd8f8dfba","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b2f2f02e965f32b4557aadee100fcabef244554a","tid":1434914,"uid":2419,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨 我唔撚會睇你打乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"而家啲post咁多真假<br />\n唔整個咁嘅標題點叫到你地入黎喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好嬲睇下先啦"},{"pid":"6fca2b1ecccbda4a9c0b46fe4e6a74350703462e","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb5c842881a8494e4196b903b4c3cafcdf210b57","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6007cd74dd4a7ea9893ead3018bbfcf8819cdb7","tid":1434914,"uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e2a1f3bf63de296a04f79183c1f8e60589add5","tid":1434914,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"而家係連登理性分析下就比人屌分化同三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-0